  <entry>
    <title>Contrail Online发布！</title>
    <link href="/2022/09/05/%E5%8F%AF%E8%BE%BE%E9%B8%ADOnline%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%EF%BC%81/"/>
    <url>/2022/09/05/%E5%8F%AF%E8%BE%BE%E9%B8%ADOnline%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%EF%BC%81/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h3><p>Contrail机器人（原可达鸭机器人，下面均命名为Contrail机器人）QQ机器人无疑是成功的，但是由于必须要把Javascript的脚本挂在服务器或者电脑上，非常的繁琐。所以，我制作了ContrailOnline。</p><h3 id="ContrailOnline"><a href="#ContrailOnline" class="headerlink" title="ContrailOnline"></a>ContrailOnline</h3><p>初代Contrail机器人是Node.JS编写的，然而ContrailOnline是基于Hexo 由 Markdown，HTML和Javascript混合编写的。</p><p>比较一下界面吧，</p><p>这是初代Contrail的交互界面 <input value="签到"><button>发送</button></p><p>这是Contrail的交互界面 <button>签到</button></p><p>这是初代Contrail的菜单</p><figure class="highlight stata"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs stata">    菜单<br>零.限时挑战<br>      1.Creeper?(NNNEEEWWW)<br>      内容是和Contrail对歌，对的歌是《Creeper？Aw <span class="hljs-keyword">man</span>&#x27;》，挑战成功金币+1000！！！<br>      2.Creeper试听<br><br>一.热门<br>      1.签到(Remade)<br>      2.一言(Remade)<br>二.迈阿密西西比特币<br>      1.财产 / 我的 / 档案<br>      2.商店<br>      3.抽奖<br>      4.看<span class="hljs-keyword">ta</span> / 看<span class="hljs-keyword">ta</span>档案 / 看<span class="hljs-keyword">ta</span>财产<br>三.工具箱<br>      1.翻译<br>      2.AI<br>      3.发言榜(Remade)<br>四.娱乐<br>      1.音乐<br>      2.猜拳<br>      3.骗我(Remade)<br>      4.拍拍我<br>      5.moo<br>      6.<span class="hljs-keyword">do</span><br>五.自动化<br>      1.早起<br>      2.夜深人静<br>      3.今天你努力了吗<br>      4.B站视频(New)<br>六.关于我<br>      1.源码<br>      2.许可证<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这是ContrailOnline的<br><img src="/img/202295-1.jpg" alt="Contrail菜单"></p><p>ContrailOnline因为可以通过JS编写所以也可以轻松移植初代的功能,比如签到<br><img src="/img/202295-2.jpg" alt="签到"></p><p>刚进入时有欢迎的弹窗<br><img src="/img/202295-3.jpg" alt="欢迎"></p><p>个人主页更加美观<br><img src="/img/202295-4.jpg" alt="个人主页"><br><img src="/img/202295-5.jpg" alt="个人主页"></p><p>还有为了防止清理浏览器数据而丢失存档,Online还加入了存档码和恢复存档的功能.</p><h3 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h3><p>ContrailOnline也算是再重置了一遍Contrail初代,还有许多要改进的地方.如有不好的地方,就尽管告诉我</p><p><a href='/psyduck/'> ContrailOnline链接</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
